[[Category:Japanese language|ゆうびんきょく]]
{{ja-kanjitab|郵|便|局}}
===Etymology===
[[郵便]] ''postal service'' + [[局]] ''office''

===Noun===
{{ja-noun|k|hira=ゆうびんきょく|rom=yūbinkyoku}}
# [[post office]]; [[postal centre]]

====Derived terms====
